**Balance transfer** moves your existing home loan from a higher-interest lender to one offering a lower rate. For example, refinancing a ₹40 lakh loan from 9.5% to 8.5% can save over ₹5 lakh in total interest. However, there are processing fees (0.25–1%) and potential stamp duty costs — this calculator shows whether the switch is financially worth it.
